<div class="research bow">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="text-wrapper">
      <article>
        <h3>Research | Form</h3>
        <p>
          I started by getting an idea for goggles’ current surface treatment.
          As I conceptualized the type of forms I wanted to tackle,
          I turned to the organic transitions of bone structures for inspiration.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
    <div class="bg">
    </div>
  </div>
